    "Building upon existing research achievements, the paper identifies several directions for future exploration in this field:(1) Optimizing Intrinsic Dimensionality: Despite existing research efforts in optimizing the intrinsic dimensionality of LoRA model weight matrices, there's still room for better understanding how to allocate intrinsic dimensions during the training of downstream task models to enhance training performance.",
    "Achieving this effectively remains a challenge.",
    "(2) Combining and Optimizing Multiple Fine-Tuning Techniques: Since LoRA is not in conflict with many other fine-tuning techniques, exploring how to rationally combine and optimize various techniques to achieve significantly better results offers a promising avenue for research.Figure 2.2Figure 2.",
    "Process of GloRA.",
